---
title: BBQ Chicken & Creamy Potato Salad with Pear Slaw
description: Tender chicken gets a lightly spiced Louisiana coating, with a creamy potato salad and fresh pear slaw to round out the meal. The real treat will be the BBQ sauce glaze to add an extra smokey taste to the chicken.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quick-bbq-chicken-creamy-potato-salad-26f71a71.jpg
